# Moves the arm to a named preset from preset_poses_sim.yaml/_real.yaml —
# e.g. "home", "standby", or "cal_ready". Prefers a joint-value preset
# (setJointValueTarget — pins the exact IK branch, no ambiguity) if one is
# loaded for name; otherwise falls back to the preset's Cartesian pose
# (setPoseTarget) if one is loaded instead. Fails if NEITHER a joint-value
# nor a Cartesian preset exists for name — never consults TF (unlike
# ~/get_standoff_pose) — see TrajectoryPlanner::planAndExecuteToPreset.
string name
---
bool success
string message